metadata.name: The Enchanting
metadata.description:
Svetlana Inac - The Women II

The Enchanting, 2022.

“The enchanting lives in her own green world, with her pure beauty and thoughts without seeing the good or bad of life.”

•	Oil on canvas

•	40x30cm (15.74x11.81inch)

•	1/1  Edition

__________________________________________________

The collector may choose to have the NFT version or the physical version of the artwork and depending on the choice the other edition will no longer exist.
